race.description: Bendigo Bank St Arnaud Mdn Plate
race.comment: SHAME ON SUE (5) pushed forward last time and boxed on to finish half a length away in second over 1175m at Manangatang. Has her share of ability. Hard to beat in this suitable race. SECRET GLORY (9) contested a Group 3 race earlier in her career and while she hasn't lived up to the early hype, this is well within her grasp. Took advantage of the good draw and raced on the pace last start then boxed on well to finish third, beaten 1.2 lengths, over 1200m at Murtoa. FROSTY NIGHT (4) failed to figure again last time over 1430m at Naracoorte, beaten 5 lengths into fifth. Should park just off the speed. Will give backers a great sight. The form of MELROSE (8) doesn't read great on paper, but this is a significant class drop on recent assignments. Only needs to run up to those efforts, especially the third placing two back, to be a chance here.
